item.description:
Meet for Dinner
Entertainment: Begins @9:15 pm
Band: Racky Thomas Blues Band
www.therackythomasband.com/

Join us for an evening of socializing/dinner and enjoying one of the Best Blues
Bands you will ever hear! The StrangeBrew Tavern is rated the "best place in
NH to have a beer"..the food is good; the energy is high and the Band will blow
you away!
item.how_to_find_us: Organizers for this event are Karen and Suzie. :-) Thanks Ladies!
